                     <interp inst="t18360815-1960-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="stealingFromMaster"></interp> for stealing, on the 2nd of Au<lb></lb>gust, 1 sovereign, and 1 half-sovereign, the monies of <persName id="t18360815-name-1143" type="victimName">
